public static interface OnixComposite.OnixDataCompositeUncommon extends OnixComposite
Fundamental interface in Jonix object model, representing an ONIX Composite that contains only ONIX Elements (i.e. no nested composites). This composite is unique to specific version of ONIX, and isn't common to all.
